FUNCTION getValue-itemfg RETURNS CHARACTER
  ( BUFFER ipb-oe-relh FOR oe-relh,BUFFER ipb-oe-rell FOR oe-rell, ipc-field AS CHAR ) :
/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Purpose:  Take a buffer and field name as string and return the value
    Notes:  
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
